description: Move emr out of preview mode.
Fix serialization of several s3 api commands. (`issue botocore 193 <https://github.com/boto/botocore/pull/196>`__)
Fix issue for unnecessarily resyncing files on windows machines. (`issue 843 <https://github.com/aws/aws-cli/issues/843>`__)
Fix issue where keys were being decoded twice when syncing between buckets. (`issue 862 <https://github.com/aws/aws-cli/pull/862>`__)
